# Risk Assessment

| Issue | Severity | Business Impact |
|------|----------|-----------------|
| Plain-text passwords | 🔴 Critical | Critical |
| Missing username validation | 🟠 Medium | Medium |
| Weak email validation | 🟡 Low | Low |
| Linear duplicate lookup | 🟡 Low | Medium |

---

# Recommended Improvements

## High Priority

- Hash passwords before storing them.
- Validate empty usernames.
- Return descriptive errors or raise exceptions.

---

## Medium Priority

- Separate validation into helper functions.
- Improve email validation.
- Replace the in-memory list with persistent storage.

---

## Low Priority

- Add type hints.
- Add documentation.
- Improve automated test coverage.
- Add logging for registration events.

